<div class="wrap-inner"><!-- breadcrumb removed -->
<h1>Global Health and IP</h1><!-- content begin -->
<div class="content">
<div class="main">
<p class="lead">Scientific and technological innovation has contributed to significant advances in public health. The challenge for policymakers is to establish an environment that stimulates health innovation while ensuring widespread access to new, more effective products to address unmet global health needs.</p>
<p class="lead">WIPO’s Global Challenges program seeks to raise awareness and understanding of the complex linkages between global health and access to medical technologies, innovation, technology transfer and trade. The goal is to leverage intellectual property (IP) as a tool that contributes to meeting the world’s most pressing health needs.</p>
</div>
<div class="complementary">
<div class="box">
<p class="featured">Featured</p>
<figure><img src="/export/sites/www/shared/pics/trilateral-20231114-845.jpg" alt="trilateral-20231114-845" />
<figcaption class="credit">(Image: Emmanuel&nbsp;Berrod)</figcaption>
</figure>
<h3><a href="/policy/en/news/global_health/2023/news_0022.html">WHO, WIPO, WTO Symposium Highlights Interrelatedness of Climate Change and Human Health</a></h3>
</div>
</div>
</div>
