<h2>Come Explore IP for a Healthier World: Ten Years of WIPO Re:Search Advancing Global Health (Archived)</h2>
<div class="cols cols--two">
<div class="col">
<figure><a href="http://ocms.wipo.int/library/en/health-exhibition.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img alt="research-virtual-exhibition-845" src="http://ocms.wipo.int/shared/pics/hero/gl_health_exhibit_welcome_hero_845.jpg" /></a></figure>
