<p>A WIPO Virtual Exhibition hosted by the WIPO Knowledge Center that takes a close-up look at how IP and ingenuity fuel an innovative public-private partnership tackling some of the world’s most devastating diseases.</p>
<p><a class="btn call-to-action" href="http://ocms.wipo.int/library/en/health-exhibition.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Archived version</a></p>
